SY215 JHMCS: Quantity and unit prices in FY18-FYDP adjusted to reflect revised negotiated contract pricing and Life Cycle Cost Estimate. Night Vision Units are contracted via a Sole Source contract with the vendor. Unit costs and quantities vary due to quantity based step-ladder pricing which results in Economy of Scale unit cost savings for higher quantities procured and increased unit costs for lower quantities procured. Additional savings from Non-Recurring used to procure 28 additional units in FY16. FY18 Baseline unit cost decreased due to procuring OCO units and Baseline units on a single contract action.
